Package: parSim
Type: Package
Title: Parallel Simulation Studies
Version: 0.1
Author: Sacha Epskamp
Maintainer: Sacha Epskamp <mail@sachaepskamp.com>
Description: Perform flexible simulation studies using one or multiple computer cores.
             The package is set up to be usuable on high-performance clusters in addition
             to being run locally, see examples on github.com/SachaEpskamp/parSim
Imports: dplyr, parallel, methods
Suggests: ggplot2, tidyr
License: GPL-2
